{'Location': ' Sy No. No 98/13-B, Gaura Waddo, Calangute, Calangute, Goa, India, 403516', 'overall_rating': '9.0', 'Name': 'HALF Hotel, Calangute', 'reviews': [{'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Exceptional‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Very nice room, the staff is very nice also and very helpful. We would definitely recommend this hotel.'}, {'Review_Rating': '9.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Superb‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'This is a very good hotel tucked into quiet and posh neighborhood of Calangute in Goa. The hotel is managed by a smart guy who comes and meet every morning all customers around breakfast time to ensure their stay is pleasant and nice . The beach is around 15 mins walk and so is market to buy stuff like booz or grocery . There are many restaurant around to eat . The hotel has a cute little pool to keep you cool in a hot afternoon and also have a nice common area to relax and laze around with a big book shelf to read from . WIFI is nice . The beds are comfortable and rooms are clean . The hotel staff is very supportive to guide you or help you with anything you need. They give you few decent options to choose from in breakfast and prepare them in onsite kitchen . However this kitchen would not prepare anything else during the day for lunch or dinner . Although you can use the big refrigerator to keep your stuff in case your room mini fridge is not good enough for you .Overall a good value for money boutique hotel with a modern and cool vibe to it.'}, {'Review_Rating': '8.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Very good‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'The hotel is nice and staff is very good'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Lovely‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Lovely stay here, Jitu was brilliant and helped us with everything we needed including renting a scooter. Rooms are spacious and clean, would definitely recommend for a relaxing couple of days.'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Clean, friendly, comfortable‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'A very nice stay. Staff were extremely friendly & helpful, exceeding expectations. The room and bed were comfortable. Everything was supplied. A quiet location with a small walk to the main street. Probably hard to find a better (at this price..)'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'One of the best stay in CALANGUTE‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Good Staff, very helpful, couple friendly;
vehicle arrangement also done by them;
near to beach; good service; housekeeping on request;'}, {'Review_Rating': '5.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Nice stay in a quiet place away from the usual chaos‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Stagg, clean toilets, just enough fixed breakfast,  rental scooter availability within the hotel, quietness, no chaos area'}, {'Review_Rating': '9.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Superb‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'The property is a short walk from Calangute beach and a short drive to Baga beach and Baga central. The hotel is secluded from the busy Main Street. the staff were great and the breakfast was too. staff all very friendly and willing to go out of their way to help'}, {'Review_Rating': '9.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Wonderful‚Äù', 'Review_Body': 'Deluxe Junior Suite is one of the comfortable stay which we experienced. This room has a special appearance of living room in the lower part and an attic level which makes it look cool and classy. We felt at home. The staff were very cooperative and jovial.'}, {'Review_Rating': '10.0', 'Review_Heading': 'Fantastic boutique hotel for tailored stay in North Goa.‚Äù', 'Review_Body': "Half Hotel is a fantastic boutique hotel tucked away in northern Goa in Calangute. 

It is run by a staff of 5-6 people headed up by Jitu. From arrival to checkout and more, the staff have been fantastic. They go out of their way to accommodate reasonable breakfast request. They were able to help with advice on local tourism and help book cabs for wherever we wanted to go. All in all, they were fantastic. 

We also had the pleasure of meeting the owner, Charles. Like his team, Charles is also excellent as a host, providing a swathe of various activities and a full range of itinerary options. Moreover, on my arrival to Goa, I had a medical issue relating to back problems. Charles immediately requested for a physician to come in and help, and that made the difference to ensure I could go about enjoying my holiday as opposed to being bed bound. 

The hotel itself is not massive, so it doesn't take 10 mins to access your room. The pool is lovely and clean, with shade and chairs to sit in the sun. Within the rooms, towels are provided and an assortment of soaps and shower gels. The balcony has a good pool view, but note, you can also see the main road etc. The room is clean, and the odd mosquito or two can be warded off easily with the repellent. The front desk were happy to provide extra repellents on demand. 

In general the room is incredibly clean and tidy and pleasant to stay in. The apartment with 2 double beds doesn't have a separating door FYI, just that it is up a set of stairs. 

In general this hotel is a fantastic stay and close to lots of local tourist opportunities. 10/10 would stay again!"}], 'price': '3,160', 'img_link': 'https://q-xx.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max500/292348971.jpg?k=b73fcb5e817492aafedb895f4d6be1608afea2798d689ad60f6e9df588edeea9&o=', 'room_size': '23m¬≤', 'amenities': ['Mountain view', 'Shower and bathtub', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Hair dryer', 'Toiletries', 'Towels', 'Walk-in shower', 'Board games/puzzles', 'Books/DVDs/music for children', 'Free Wi-Fi in all rooms!', 'Pool facilities', 'Satellite/cable channels', 'Telephone', 'Adapter', 'Air conditioning', 'Fan', 'Hand sanitizer', 'Linens', 'Sleep comfort items', 'Wake-up service', 'Coffee/tea maker', 'Free bottled water', 'Refrigerator', 'Tile/marble flooring', 'Trash cans', 'Closet', 'Clothes rack', 'Ironing facilities', 'Accessible by stairs', 'Individual air conditioning', 'Safety/security feature'], 'city': 'Goa', 'link': 'https://agoda.com/en-gb/half-hotel-calangute/hotel/all/goa-in.html?finalPriceView=1&isShowMobileAppPrice=false&cid=1844104&numberOfBedrooms=&familyMode=false&adults=2&children=0&rooms=1&maxRooms=0&checkIn=2023-03-18&isCalendarCallout=false&childAges=&numberOfGuest=0&missingChildAges=false&travellerType=1&showReviewSubmissionEntry=false&currencyCode=INR&isFreeOccSearch=false&isCityHaveAsq=false&los=1&searchrequestid=18d700e7-651f-4402-abd4-aa9f328d75d8'}

